        %h3.ui.header Our Mission
        %p
          We are a team of people under the auspices of The Journey Church who
          are sponsoring a Syrian refugee family or families to settle in
          Moncton or surrounding area.
        %p
          Sponsoring a family involves providing accommodations, furnishings,
          clothing, food, and other necessities of life, for the first 12
          months of their life here. We will also assist the family to adjust
          to life in Moncton, with a goal of helping them to be self-sufficient
          by the end of the 12 months.
