        %h3 How Can I Help?
        %p
          There are two major ways you can help.
        %p
          Firstly, there will be many
          practical tasks that will need to be completed both before and after
          the family arrives.  Some of the opportunities include:
        %ul
          %li Obtaining any necessary clothing
          %li Helping refugees learn how and where to shop
          %li Obtaining medical, dental, and eye care
          %li
            Help with transportation, employment opportunities, socialization,
            and many other needs.
        %p
          If you would like to help in these ways, please email us at
          %a(href="mailto:partnersofhoperefugeeresponse@gmail.com") partnersofhoperefugeeresponse@gmail.com
          and indicate particular areas of
          interest.
        %p
          Secondly there is a monetary need.
        %p
          The financial commitment to
          support a refugee family will be approximately $25,000
          (depending on the size of the family).  Donations can be made to
          The Journey Church, designating “Syrian Refugee Response”,
          and are tax-deductible.
